@NODE why
@TITLE "Why requesters"

  If you get an error requester  from  APlayer, and  you  don't  understand
  what's  going on, press the @{b}WHY@{ub} gadget in the requester. This gives you a
  brief description of the error, and suggestions on how to correct it.
@ENDNODE
